{
  "id": "class_0062",
  "name": "Exile's Gauntlet",
  "title_completion": "an Exile's Gauntlet",
  "flavor_text": "The Mad King signed your Exile Writ with a flourish and a laugh, then handed you his gauntlet as a parting joke. Now you wander the windswept corridors between thrones, delivering his decrees to courts that no longer recognize his seal. Every strike lands like a royal proclamation \u2014 loud, absolute, and utterly unhinged.",
