    {
      "id": "skill_001461",
      "name": "Gauntlet Strike Censure",
      "role": "damage_over_time",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "melee_strike",
      "energy_cost": 10.7,
      "cooldown_seconds": 4.5,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "bleed",
          "params": {
            "tick_damage": 1009,
            "duration_seconds": 4.9
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The blow lands with the weight of a king's unspoken displeasure, and the wound bleeds as if the body itself is being slowly erased from court record. Wind hisses through the throne room as the victim staggers, hemorrhaging legitimacy and life alike."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_001462",
      "name": "Gauntlet Edict",
      "role": "primary_attack",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "melee_strike",
      "energy_cost": 8.1,
      "cooldown_seconds": 0.9,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "damage",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 841,
            "element": "physical",
            "pierce": 1,
            "multishot": 3
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The king's fury given weight and velocity, a decree that does not ask for compliance. It arrives before the sound of its own sending."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_001463",
      "name": "Gauntlet Strike Decree",
      "role": "damage_over_time",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "melee_strike",
      "energy_cost": 21.4,
      "cooldown_seconds": 4.6,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "bleed",
          "params": {
            "tick_damage": 1009,
            "duration_seconds": 4.9
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The Mad King's fist descends in a ring of howling wind, and those caught within find their veins opened by the edict of his displeasure. The court watches in silence as the bleeding begins, slow and inevitable as royal law."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_001464",
      "name": "Wind Through Empty Thrones",
      "role": "mobility",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "dash_attack",
      "energy_cost": 17.4,
      "cooldown_seconds": 6.3,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "buff_dodge",
          "params": {
            "percent": 0.16,
            "duration_seconds": 6.7
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "damage",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 0,
            "element": "physical"
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The warrior vanishes between one heartbeat and the next, leaving only a cold draft where the Mad King's censure could not follow. Movement becomes answer, absence becomes armor."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_001465",
      "name": "Gauntlet Wind Exile",
      "role": "mobility",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "leap_strike",
      "energy_cost": 12.1,
      "cooldown_seconds": 10.7,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "buff_dodge",
          "params": {
            "percent": 0.23,
            "duration_seconds": 8.9
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The throne room howls as you throw yourself aside, the mad king's decree scattering like parchment in a gale. For a breathless moment, his court cannot touch you \u2014 you belong to the wind, not his writ."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_001466",
      "name": "Gauntlet of Mad Winds",
      "role": "burst_damage",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "melee_arc",
      "energy_cost": 28.5,
      "cooldown_seconds": 6.1,
